ROOT CAUSE ANALYSIS
Primary Issue: [e.g., Retention & Expansion] 
Symptoms: 
NRR 95% (should be 100%) CR 5% monthly (should be <3%) Expansion revenue only 10% of MRR (should be 20-30%) 
Diagnosis: [e.g., Customers are churning before they expand. Onboarding is weak, no clear upsell paths.] 
Impact: 
LOST_MRR [Calculate churn impact]
